title: Class `Session`
description: Persistent storage using sessions.
...

### Set

~~~ .xmp.php
Session::set($key, $value = "");
~~~

Set a session:

~~~ .php
Session::set('my_session', 'the value');
~~~

### Reset

~~~ .xmp.php
Session::reset($key = null);
~~~

Remove a session:

~~~ .php
Session::reset('my_session');
~~~

Remove multiple sessions:

~~~ .php
Session::reset(['my_session', 'your_session', 'our_session']);
~~~

Remove all sessions:

~~~ .php
Session::reset();
~~~

### Get

~~~ .xmp.php
Session::get($key = null, $fail = "");
~~~

Get a session:

~~~ .php
Session::get('my_session', '#');
~~~

Get all sessions:

~~~ .php
Session::get();
~~~